 {{ill|Ōtoshi Shrine (Kasai, Hokujō)|ja|大歳神社 (加西市北条町北条)|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōtoshi Shrine (Kasai, Hokujō)|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in Hokujō, Kasai City, Hyōgo Prefecture. * {{ill|Ōtoshi Shrine (Fukusaki, Yachigusa)|ja|大歳神社 (福崎町八千種)|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōtoshi Shrine (Fukusaki, Yachigusa)|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in Yachigusa, Fukusaki Town, Hyōgo Prefecture. * {{ill|Ōtoshi Shrine (Kamikawa, Fukumoto)|ja|大歳神社 (神河町福本)|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōtoshi Shrine (Kamikawa, Fukumoto)|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in Fukumoto, Kamikawa Town, Hyōgo Prefecture. * {{ill|Ōtoshi Shrine (Kamikawa, Kashio)|ja|大歳神社 (神河町柏尾)|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōtoshi Shrine (Kamikawa, Kashio)|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in Kashio, Kamikawa Town, Hyōgo Prefecture. * {{ill|Ōtoshi Shrine (Shinonsen)|ja|大歳神社 (新温泉町)|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōtoshi Shrine (Shinonsen)|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in Shinonsen Town, Hyōgo Prefecture. * {{ill|Ōtoshi Shrine (Kinokawa, Momoyama-chō)|ja|大歳神社 (紀の川市桃山町)|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōtoshi Shrine (Kinokawa, Momoyama-chō)|qq=}} - Located in Momoyama-chō, Kinokawa City, Wakayama Prefecture. * {{ill|Ōtoshi Shrine (Hidaka District, Inami Town)|ja|大歳神社 (日高郡印南町)|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōtoshi Shrine (Hidaka District, Inami Town)|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in Inamihara, Inami Town, Hidaka District, Wakayama Prefecture. * {{ill|Ōtoshi Shrine (Shimonoseki)|ja|大歳神社 (下関市)|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōtoshi Shrine (Shimonoseki)|qq=}} - Located in Shimonoseki City, Yamaguchi Prefecture. * {{ill|Ten'ōgū Ōtoshi Shrine|ja|天王宮大歳神社|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ten'ōgū Ōtoshi Shrine|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in Tenno-chō, Hamamatsu City, Shizuoka Prefecture. * {{ill|Saminaga Shrine|en|Saminaga Shrine|WD=Q17209205|lt=Samino Shrine|1=Saminaga Shrine}} - Formerly known as "Ōtoshi Shrine," a subordinate shrine of {{ill|Izawa-no-miya|en|Iza